"With WiredTiger, MongoDB utilizes both the WiredTiger cache and the "
"filesystem cache."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/extracts/wt-cache-default-setting.rst:6
msgid ""
"Starting in MongoDB 3.2, the WiredTiger cache, by default, will use the "
"larger of either:"
msgstr ""

